evals.prompt: Fetch the names of all countries with an average precipitation of greater than 326.
evals.expected_query: SELECT DISTINCT country FROM world_bank_development_indicators WHERE avg_precipitation > 326;

evals.prompt: Get all countries where the life expectancy is above 39 years old.
evals.expected_query: SELECT DISTINCT country FROM world_bank_development_indicators WHERE life_expectancy_at_birth > 39

evals.prompt: List all the countries whose life expectancy is above 39 years old and the population is over 5 million.
evals.expected_query: SELECT DISTINCT country FROM world_bank_development_indicators WHERE life_expectancy_at_birth > 39 AND population > 5000000

evals.prompt: List all the countries whose life expectancy is above 39 years old whose birth rate is over 50 per 1000.
evals.expected_query: SELECT country FROM world_bank_development_indicators WHERE life_expectancy_at_birth > 39 AND birth_rate > 50
